@startuml
|User|
start
:Clicks "Register";
|System|
:Displays registration form;
|User|
:Enters details (name, email, password, etc.);
:Submits the form;
|System|
:Validates the information;
:Send verification email;
|User|
:Clicks verification link in the email;
|System|
:Confirms email verification;
:Completes registration;
stop
@enduml